---
title: Fiesta Chicken Tacos With a Spicy Apple Cabbage Slaw and Lime Crema
description: There’s a party going on in these tacos and all the best ingredients were invited: easy-to-cook chicken stir-fry strips, warm Southwest spices, and an apple cabbage slaw that’s as crisp and cool as it gets. And because every party benefits from a little something extra to get it going, the filling gets drizzled in a zesty lime crema that’ll make you feel the way you do when your favorite jam comes on. So what are you waiting for? You know these tacos are gonna be a rockin’ time.
